## Subspace.shouldEnsureConsistentVersions() method

> This API is provided as a beta preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

Gets the ensureConsistentVersions property from the common-versions.json config file, or from the rush.json file if it isn't defined in common-versions.json
